What his story will be. I reckon
he'll confine himself to the nervous
origin of her recent illness. His notes
will be touthful, but what he leaves out
will matter mort. Strange how just
then Philip
was so certain that Nicholas
would never betray him. He loved
Sandra too
deeply to ruin her
future happines. Had evereiraum-
stances conspired to cummingly?
Philip's zirit soared.
